Features Implemented
Full CRUD Operations:

Create: Add new tasks with title, description, due date, and category

Read: Display all tasks grouped by category

Update: Edit any task field

Delete: Remove tasks

Task Attributes:

Title (required)

Description (optional)

Due date (optional, with date picker)

Category (default categories: Work, Personal, Study)

Completion status (toggle checkbox)

Category Management:

Tasks are grouped by category

Ability to add new categories

Category selector when creating/editing tasks

UI Features:

Material-UI for modern, responsive design

Date picker for due dates

Completion status shown with strikethrough

Confirmation dialogs for actions

Additional Features:

Task count per category

Form validation

Error handling

Responsive layout